{"id": "1463147201017417760", "channel_id": "1462880724616220868", "type": 19, "author_id": "212031841786527764", "author_name": "chinkeeyong", "author_bot": false, "content": "since you only get 1 copy of the character, the best characters at e0 are castor and clementine\n\ne0 castor is a great shielder and does enough damage that he can carry a team of 3 bricks early game\n\ne0 clementine is a versatile support who produces tons of keyflare and STR, and has unique debuffs that stack with weakness/vulnerable\n\nthe other characters are all mid to bad at e0 and you will have to spend months investing your prototype horizons into them until they become good", "timestamp": "2026-01-20T12:24:36.683000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["984920307158630481"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1462880724616220868", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1462880724616220868", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Who should I choose for the character selector?", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
